::CyberShark::

    He only recived this part of the message. "But where wi=
ll they be-----" The rest was static. He tried to send a message through to=
 her. "I'm in the Destron base as of now, I don't think that I'm going to b=
e able to get through the static for a while."
    Magmatron's holo image s=
till was before him, just staring. CyberShark turned and left, he didn't kn=
ow who Magmatron had left in charge, but he hoped it wasn't Bobertron.
    =
He left the base and did a quick scan for the Temporal Gate. He found it.
 =
   "Battera, Magmatron left the planet," CyberShark said, sure that the sta=
tic wouldn't affect the comm system once outside of the Destron base. "He s=
aid for me to go through it and join him, but don't worry I'm not gonna. Ca=
n I join you at the Maximal base?"
